    {
        "url": "/quotes/frances_ogrady_459506",
        "quote": "The difficulty for the Government is there's this ideological straitjacket of the market will provide, let the market rip and everything will work out... It's back to trickle-down economics, which, it's plain to see, have not delivered.",
